re snudd veldig dumt til med tanke p\u00e5 trafikken. Man kunne eventuelt ha lagt det ned p\u00e5 bakken, sier han."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "74e300676673f40fb4d413b96361713b9885dd2cdfdc839f2dda4e730fb68e26"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-02-11T19:36:33.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Motstridende budskap p\u00e5 Tiller gir bilister hodebry. N\u00e5 lover Vegvesenet bot og bedring."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article6711629.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/20121122_120211.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/10a7a7739ca94391e4e09af41b0b257024bdaed1.jpg?596cc363"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["- Jeg forst\u00e5r at folk blir forvirret -adressa.no", "Om lag 40 meter mellom skiltene", "- Bare satt til side"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "10a7a7739ca94391e4e09af41b0b257024bdaed1"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bak kj\u00f8pesenteret", "vegvesen", "forst\u00e5r", "kj\u00f8pesenteret", "bilister", "forbudsskiltet", "motstridende budskap", "kj\u00f8re", "forvirret"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["vegvesenet", "\u00f8ysand", "statens", "tillertorget", "tiller"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["roger gjeldnes", "svein nordvik"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondh